=\"color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;\"><strong>GIÁ ĐÃ BAO GỒM VAT.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600; font-size: medium;\"><strong>MIỄN PHÍ VẬN CHUYỂN TOÀN QUỐC.</strong></span></p>            </div>\n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n', 'Tai Nghe Sennheiser PX 80', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tai-nghe-sennheiser-px-80', '', '', '2018-05-11 05:18:08', '2018-05-11 05:18:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tainghetot/product/tai-nghe-sennheiser-px-80/', 0, 'product', '', 0),
